NeedMaterial.Name: Refined Botanic Powder
NeedMaterial.Description: A culinary byproduct primarily used for crafting fish bait.
NeedMaterial.Description2$english: Made by simmering knotted plant stems and buds, then sun-drying and grinding them into a fine powder—highly attractive to fish and perfect for bait-making!

NeedMaterial.Description2$english: In their free-living state, buds exhibit no discernible metabolic activity and exist in a dormant phase characterized as cryptobiosis. Upon encountering favorable environmental conditions, they resume activity and germinate into vegetative cells.
